summary: This document appears to be a Mortgage Privacy Form from Fifth Third Private Bank, detailing the requirements for borrowers to authorize the sharing of their information among Fifth Third affiliates for mortgage relationship pricing. It includes sections for borrower signatures and consent to share documentation.
keyFacts: The document is a Mortgage Privacy Form from Fifth Third Private Bank.
Borrowers are required to grant authorization for sharing their information among Fifth Third affiliates.
The form includes options for borrowers to accept or decline participation in the mortgage relationship pricing program.
There are sections for borrower signatures and dates, indicating consent.
The document emphasizes the confidentiality of the information shared among Fifth Third entities.
